{"tha-ap125:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap125:0.2":"Sereyyavagga ","tha-ap125:0.3":"3 Payasadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap125:1.1":"“Suvannavanno sambuddho, ","tha-ap125:1.2":"Battimsavaralakkhano; ","tha-ap125:1.3":"Pavana abhinikkhanto, ","tha-ap125:1.4":"Bhikkhusanghapurakkhato. ","tha-ap125:2.1":"Mahacca kamsapatiya, ","tha-ap125:2.2":"vaddhetva payasam aham; ","tha-ap125:2.3":"Ahutim yitthukamo so, ","tha-ap125:2.4":"upanesim balim aham. ","tha-ap125:3.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap125:3.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap125:3.3":"Cankamam susamarulho, ","tha-ap125:3.4":"ambare anilayane. ","tha-ap125:4.1":"Tanca acchariyam disva, ","tha-ap125:4.2":"abbhutam lomahamsanam; ","tha-ap125:4.3":"Thapayitva kamsapatim, ","tha-ap125:4.4":"vipassim abhivadayim. ","tha-ap125:5.1":"Tuvam devosi sabbannu, ","tha-ap125:5.2":"sadeve sahamanuse; ","tha-ap125:5.3":"Anukampam upadaya, ","tha-ap125:5.4":"patiganha mahamuni. ","tha-ap125:6.1":"Patiggahesi bhagava, ","tha-ap125:6.2":"sabbannu lokanayako; ","tha-ap125:6.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap125:6.4":"sattha loke mahamuni. ","tha-ap125:7.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap125:7.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap125:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap125:7.4":"payasassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap125:8.1":"Ekatalisito kappe, ","tha-ap125:8.2":"buddho namasi khattiyo; ","tha-ap125:8.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap125:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap125:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap125:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap125:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap125:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma payasadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap125:11.1":"Payasadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}